That gets you fully away from the confusing “bootstrap generated” naming and lines everything up with the ownership model:

configure server  → group_vars/all/aerolitctl_server_generated.yml
configure ansible → group_vars/all/aerolitctl_ansible_generated.yml + inventory/90_aerolitctl.ini
deploy server     → consumes generated vars and runs playbooks